Class Meal

  • java.lang.Object
    • Meal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Meal
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class that represents a meal eaten by user. A user can have as many meals as he wants a day and can change or delete it. A meal can have multiple foods.
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Marcelo Portella
    See Also:
